videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo is left open behind the 3-point line and knocks down the triple from the wing.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis cans the early triple) 2020/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis cans the early triple

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo goes full extension and flushes home the huge one-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis comes charging down the lane for huge dunk) 2020/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis comes charging down the lane for huge dunk

videos.description: Alec Burks gets into the lane and leaves the ball for Nerlens Noel for the simple two-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Burks dishes to Noel for easy dunk) 2020/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burks dishes to Noel for easy dunk

videos.description: Mitchell Robinson gathers the pass, goes up and dunks it right on Brook Lopez.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Robinson crams one on Lopez) 2020/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Robinson crams one on Lopez

videos.description: Donte DiVincenzo knocks down the 3-pointer as he absorbs the contact.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (DiVincenzo drains the 3 plus the foul) 2020/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: DiVincenzo drains the 3 plus the foul

videos.description: Julius Randle drives down the lane and finishes the shot plus the foul as the third quarter closes.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Randle muscles in the and-1 to end the third) 2020/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Randle muscles in the and-1 to end the third

videos.description: RJ Barrett throws the lob up to Mitchell Robinson who flushes it home with one hand.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Barrett, Robinson combine for alley-oop) 2020/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Barrett, Robinson combine for alley-oop

videos.description: Thanasis Antetokounmpo and Iggy Brazdeikis have to be separated by officials after getting tangled under the basket.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Thanasis Antetokounmpo and Brazdeikis have to be separated) 2020/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Thanasis Antetokounmpo and Brazdeikis have to be separated

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo goes for 27 points, 13 rebounds and 5 assists, but the Bucks struggle and fall to the Knicks 130-110.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Giannis goes for 27-point double-double in Bucks’ loss to Knicks) 2020/12/27 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Giannis goes for 27-point double-double in Bucks' loss to Knicks

videos.description: Julius Randle scores 29 points while Elfrid Payton goes for 27 as the Knicks dominate the Bucks 130-110.
